Rex Banner is truly a one stop shop. As a producer, songwriter, engineer, multi-instrumentalist and musical director, he brings his expansive talent to his work which spans years of commercial scoring and production. Starting as a Classical pianist he moved on to studies in Jazz composition followed by years of training in Havana's prestigious Escuela Nacional del Arte. His sound and style showcase all of his experience and refined talent as one of today's best producers for film, TV and a long list of commercial Pop artists.
